@@TJvExCheckListBox.OnMouseLeave
Summary
  Occurs when the mouse pointer moves off the list box.
Description
  Write an OnMouseLeave event handler to take specific action when the user moves the mouse off the
  list box. For example, you can use this event to undo changes that were made in an OnMouseEnter event
  handler.
See Also
  TJvExCheckListBox.OnMouseEnter

